      "width": 7200
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1- Choisir la roue \u00e0 tester",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 960,
      "top": 1320,
      "height": 330,
      "width": 3900
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2- Passer \u00e0 l'\u00e9tape 2 - D\u00e9but comptage",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 960,
      "top": 3240,
      "height": 405,
      "width": 5580
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "3- Effectuer un tour pr\u00e9cis et complet de la roue sans revenir en arri\u00e8re",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 840,
      "top": 4560,
      "height": 345,
      "width": 8040
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- D\u00e9caler le rep\u00e8re sur la roue de 1 cm",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2880,
      "top": 6840,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 4920
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "- Recommencer \u00e0 l'\u00e9tape 1",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2880,
      "top": 7080,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 5205
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "B - Si le premier r\u00e9sultat est inf\u00e9rieur \u00e0 47 dents, si le deuxi\u00e8me r\u00e9sultat est inf\u00e9rieur \u00e0 48 dents, alors la cible est d\u00e9fectueuse",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2400,
      "top": 7440,
      "height": 600,
      "width": 7680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "C - Si le r\u00e9sultat est sup\u00e9rieur \u00e0 48 dents, plus d'un tour a \u00e9t\u00e9 effectu\u00e9 ; recommencer \u00e0 l'\u00e9tape 1",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2400,
      "top": 8040,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 7680
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ">>>",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 3480,
      "top": 5160,
