     }
    },
    {
     "text": "CONTROLE HYDRAULIQUE",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "2",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2760,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 300,
      "width": 6240
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 16.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Si la PEDALE est LONGUE, moteur arr\u00e9t\u00e9, alors il y a de l'air dans le circuit primaire de freinage.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 720,
      "height": 720,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Dans ce cas NE PAS r\u00e9aliser ce cont\u00f4le MAIS r\u00e9aliser une purge classique.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(255,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 1080,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Pour tester le circuit de freinage, arr\u00e9tez le moteur puis appuyez 3 fois sur la p\u00e9dale de frein.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 1560,
      "height": 240,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "Pour r\u00e9aliser le test:",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 3000,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Si la p\u00e9dale s'enfonce toujours alors il y a de l'air dans le circuit primaire de freinage.",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 960,
      "top": 1920,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11640
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": ". Sinon le circuit de freinage est OK",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(64,0,64)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 960,
      "top": 2280,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "1 - Appuyer sur la p\u00e9dale de frein",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 600,
      "top": 3360,
      "height": 360,
      "width": 11520
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "Arial",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "2 - Une autre personne essaye de tourner une roue",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "bbox": {
